item.title: head kick
item.description: i just made a 3ft x 4ft picture of my head. it is pretty funny. especially when it is printed out. so. umm. yea. here is a 6ft x 8ft unicorn and a 10ft x 15ft valkyriemy life suddenly got incredibly complicated. you have no idea.
